steps: 
1) Search CloudFormation
2) Add the above content in a file with extension .yml
3) upload this file 
4) Will ask for key pair to choose -- Either choose an existing key or create a new key from EC2 Dashboard -- Key Pair Tab and then  choose this new key
5) Create Stack
 
An instance will be created in the EC2 instances section. 
By default SSH will not be enabled, go to the security groups -> Edit inbound rules -> Add SSH 
 
